Fix TypeScript errors in the AstroLab mobile app. Make the following changes:

## 1. Fix CampaignRedemption type - add missing fields

Read and edit the file `C:\Users\User\AstroLabDiffusion\astrolab\packages\shared\src\types\index.ts`.

Find the `CampaignRedemption` interface and replace it with this expanded version that includes the missing fields:

```typescript
export interface CampaignRedemption {
  id: string;
  campaign_id: string;
  customer_id: string;
  qr_code_id: string;
  merchant_id: string;
  redemption_token: string;
  is_redeemed: boolean;
  redeemed_at: string | null;
  expires_at: string | null;
  created_at: string;
}
```

## 2. Add CustomerScanSuccessData type

In the same file, after the `CampaignRedemption` interface, add this new interface if it doesn't already exist:

```typescript
export interface CustomerScanSuccessData {
  merchant_name: string;
  points_earned: number;
  stamps_earned: number;
  total_points: number;
  stamps_current_card: number;
  stamps_per_card: number;
  card_completed: boolean;
  card_id: string;
  offerToken?: string;
}
```

Search the file first to see if `CustomerScanSuccessData` already exists. If it does, don't add a duplicate.

## 3. Fix Button component to accept children

Read and edit `C:\Users\User\AstroLabDiffusion\astrolab\apps\mobile\src\components\ui\Button.tsx`.

Change the ButtonProps interface to also accept `children` as an alternative to `title`:

Replace the interface:
```typescript
interface ButtonProps {
  title: string;
  onPress: () => void;
```

With:
```typescript
export interface ButtonProps {
  title?: string;
  children?: React.ReactNode;
  onPress: () => void;
```

And in the destructured params, change:
```typescript
export function Button({
  title,
  onPress,
```

To:
```typescript
export function Button({
  title,
  children,
  onPress,
```

And change the text rendering from:
```tsx
        <Text style={[styles.text, { color: v.text, fontSize: s.fontSize }, textStyle]}>
          {title}
        </Text>
```

To:
```tsx
        <Text style={[styles.text, { color: v.text, fontSize: s.fontSize }, textStyle]}>
          {children ?? title}
        </Text>
```

Make sure to read each file before editing it.

